                        <p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></span></p><p><section data-source="bj.96weixin.com"><section style=" clear: both;  width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; "><section style=" border-color: rgb(17, 159, 82) rgb(11, 181, 89) rgb(15, 191, 96) rgb(177, 151, 241); margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%; border-left-width: 15px; border-left-style: solid;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section style="line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.4;   word-wrap: break-word !important; "><section style="box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;float: left;margin-top: 10px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 32px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; float: inherit; background-color: rgb(177, 151, 241);"><span style="font-family:宋体">黄疸</span></section><section style="padding: 0px; color: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important; border-left-color: rgb(177, 151, 241); border-top-width: 15px !important; border-bottom-width: 16px !important; border-left-width: 18px; border-top-style: solid !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 48px 20px 5px; font-size: 14px;"><p style="line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; color: inherit;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">新生儿黄疸是新生儿时期常见疾病，也称新生儿高胆红素血症。正常新生儿出生后<span style="font-family:Times New Roman">2-3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">天开始出现黄疸，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">4-5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">天达高峰，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">周内消退，这是由于新生儿时期胆红素生产较多，而其摄取、结合、排泄胆红素的能力仅为成人的</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">1%-2%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，因此容易出现皮肤黄疸，尤其是新生儿处于缺氧、饥饿、胎粪排出延迟、脱水等状态时加重而出现病理性黄疸，病理性黄疸的发生特点为皮肤黄疸在出生后</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">24</span><span style="font-family:宋体">小时内出现；黄疸程度程度重或者血清胆红素每日上升超过</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">㎎</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">/dl</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；黄疸持续持续时间长；黄疸退而复现，对于病理性黄疸应积极查找病因，如果血清胆红素持续升高未及时治疗，血脑屏障开放胆红素进入脑组织损伤中枢神经系统会引起严重的胆红素脑病。特别是对于存在新生儿黄疸高危因素的宝宝，我们应密切观察宝宝的黄疸出现时间、黄疸部位及范围，大小便的次数、量及性质，有无吸允无力，纳差等情况。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; color: inherit;"><br  /></p></section></section></section></section></section></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></span></p><p><section data-source="bj.96weixin.com"><section style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(177, 151, 241); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 0px; border: medium; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 1em; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(223, 37, 133); margin-top: 0px; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" data-width="100%"><section style="border-color: rgb(89, 195, 249); margin: 0px; padding: 0.6em; color: inherit; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1.2em; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(177, 151, 241);" data-brushtype="text"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>宝宝出生后，奶爸奶妈们应该如何做才能避免宝宝皮肤黄疸加重的情况出现？</strong></span></section><section style="padding: 0px; width: 0px; height: 10px; color: inherit; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; border-top-color: rgb(177, 151, 241); border-right-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-color: rgb(177, 151, 241); border-left-color: transparent !important; border-top-width: 0.8em; border-right-width: 0.8em !important; border-left-width: 0.8em !important; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid !important; border-left-style: solid !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; padding: 0px;"><section style="padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; margin: 0px; border-color: rgb(41, 11, 107);"><p style="color: inherit; line-height: 2em; white-space: normal;"><img style="width: auto !important; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" src="../assets/image/productAdmin/healthInfo/11.png" data-ratio="0.666" data-w="500" data-type="jpeg" data-s="300,640"  /><br  /></p><section style="margin: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" data-style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(127,127,127);"><p style="line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(193, 33, 101);"><span style="border-color: rgb(89, 195, 249); color: rgb(177, 151, 241);"></span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 宋体;">1 <span style="font-family: 宋体;">做好早吸吮</span>。</span></strong></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">凡是做好早吸吮工作的产妇，乳汁较充盈，其新生儿很少发生黄疸加重的现象。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 宋体;">2 做好勤吸吮。</span></strong></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">增加喂养次数，频率，可以促进肠管蠕动，促进胎便排除，又可促进正常的肠道菌群和尿量增加，从而增加结合胆红素以及光化学胆红素的产物经尿量及粪便的排除。乳汁分泌较晚的产妇，新生儿喂养不足，尿量不足，胎便延迟，以致黄疸的加重。新生儿肠腔内的胎粪约含胆红素<span style="font-family:Times New Roman">80-100</span><span style="font-family:宋体">㎎，相当于每日胆红素产生的</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">5-10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">倍，胎粪排出延迟，加重胆红素的重吸收，因此强调母乳喂养重要的同时多喂水，适时采用配方乳喂养，保证新生儿的正常生理需要，减轻和预防黄疸。</span></span><br  /></p></section></section></section></section><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><br  /></span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">母乳性黄疸为一种特殊类型的病理性黄疸，大约有<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1</span>％母乳喂养的婴儿可发生母乳性黄疸，常与生理性黄疸重叠持续不退，宝宝一般状态良好，停止母乳喂养后<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">3</span>天，如黄疸下降即可确诊。若为母乳性黄疸，嘱可继续母乳喂养，如母乳喂养后仍出现黄疸，可改为隔次母乳喂养逐步过渡到正常母乳喂养，若黄疸严重，患儿一般情况差，可考虑暂停母乳喂养，黄疸消退后再恢复母乳喂养。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">衢州市妇幼保健院新生儿科</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">汪一帆</span></p><p><br  /></p>
